Laura Eji ụra bụ ihe nkiri egwu dị mkpirikpi nke America nke 2020 nke Parker nke ụwa Finn dere, duzie, ma soro mepụta
Ndị na-eme ihe nkiri bụ Caitlin Stasey na Lew Temple
Ọ ga-emesị bụrụ ihe na-akpali akpali maka ihe nkiri egwu Finn na-eme Smile (2022); ihe na-aga ndị na eme ka n'ihu nke Stasey gosipụtara na ímé ọrụ ya n'ụzọ dị mkpirikpi.
Ka ọ na-agwa onye na-agwọ ya Dr
Parsons banyere nrọ ọjọọ na-eme ugboro ugboro nke nwoke ọjọọ na-amụmụ ọnụ ọchị mgbe niile, Laura Weaver chọpụtara na ọ ka na-ahụ nrọ ọjọọ ahụ mgbe Dr
Parson gbanwere n'ime ihe dị egwu nke chọrọ ịmanye Laura ile ya anya
N'ịjụ ile anya, Laura si n'ime ụlọ ahụ gbapụ
Ọ laghachiri mgbe obere oge gachara, na-ekwere na anụ ọhịa ahụ apụọla; Otú ọ dị, ọ pụtara na mberede n'ihu ya, na-eme ka ọ daa ara ma na-eti mkpu ka ọ na-adọkpụ ihu ya.
E gosipụtara ihe nkiri ahụ na SXSW Film ememe. N'ịgbaso ihe ịga nke ọma nke mịmụmụ ọnụ ọchị, a tọhapụrụ ya na YouTube na Nọvemba 2022.
Nightmarish Conjurings "adịghị akwado ihe nkiri ahụ ma ọ bụrụ na ị nwere nsogbu ihi ụra". Mara mma nke ukwuu nyere ya 4.5 n'ime 5. IMDb nyere ya 6.7/10, dabere na votu 756.
